subject: College Athletics
Antitrust Laws and Competition Issues
lead_paragraph: Judge Claudia Wilken of United States District Court in Oakland, Calif., denied the N.C.A.A.’s request to delay the trial on an antitrust suit filed by the former U.C.L.A. basketball player Ed O’Bannon and others.
